                  </hi>. I am the wife of Robert Criper—we live in Brook-street, Ratcliffe. I let ready-furnished lodgings—the prisoner</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183708140054"></xptr>
               <p>hired a lodging the beginning of May, at 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. a week—I knew very little of her before—I had seen her about—she brought her mother to lodge with her—she was nearly seven weeks with me—she paid me 8<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.—I gave her warning several times, because I could not get my rent—at length I went into the room and missed all these things—I have found since that she did it to keep her mother—she bad very little support.</p>
